important. But it seems like every time you come up with a great blog name, it&#8217;s already been taken by someone else. So how do you come up with a blog name that&#8217;s not only available but sounds great [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-blog-name-generators/\">8 BEST Blog Name Generators to Find the Perfect Blog Name</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16826:\"<p>Are you looking for the best blog name generators? Choosing a name for your blog is important. But it seems like every time you come up with a great blog name, it&#8217;s already been taken by someone else. So how do you come up with a blog name that&#8217;s not only available but sounds great too? Blog name generators can help. A blog name generator is a tool that will help you easily come up with blog name ideas.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll go over the best blog name generators that will help you find the best name for your blog. The best part: All of these blog name generators are free to use! </p>\n<p>Let&#8217;s get started!</p>\n<h3>Tips for Choosing a Blog Name</h3>\n<p>If you want to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-start-a-blog-step-by-step/\">start a blog</a>, one of the first steps is to choose a blog name. Picking the perfect blog name can be difficult though and you have to put a lot of thought into it. Once you choose a blog name, you&#8217;re kind of stuck with it. So, not only does your blog name have to represent your brand and who you are, but you also have to consider your future blog readers as well. The success of your blog relies in part on picking the best blog name, so choose wisely. </p>\n<p>Some tips for choosing the best name for your blog are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Keep it Short</strong> &#8211; A good blog name should be short. It&#8217;s easier for your audience to type and remember. </li>\n<li><strong>Easy to Spell</strong> &#8211; If your blog name is too difficult to spell, people will likely misspell it when trying to find you online. For this reason, avoid adding double letters, special characters, and numbers as well.</li>\n<li><strong>Use Keywords</strong> &#8211; If you&#8217;re blogging about gardening, try using the keyword &#8220;gardening&#8221; in your blog name, so users can easily find you on the web. </li>\n<li><strong>Don&#8217;t Make it Too Narrow</strong> &#8211; Choose a name that leaves your blog room to grow. For example, if you start blogging about pasta recipes and name your blog &#8220;Pasta of the Day&#8221;, in the future when you want to blog about desserts, your name won&#8217;t attract people who&#8217;re looking for dessert recipes. </li>\n<li><strong>Make it Brandable &#038; Unique</strong> &#8211; Your blog name has to stand out to readers, so pick a name that grabs their attention and sticks with them. </li>\n</ul>\n<p>Now that you know how to choose a good name for your blog, let&#8217;s get into our list of the best blog name generators to help you come up with the best blog name for you. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/domain-name-generator/\">1. IsItWP Domain Name Generator Tool</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/domain-name-generator/\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/isitwp-blog-name-generator.jpg\" alt=\"isitwp-domain-name-generator\" width=\"740\" height=\"285\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230441\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/isitwp-blog-name-generator.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/isitwp-blog-name-generator-300x116.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Our own tool, the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/domain-name-generator/\">IsItWP Domain Name Generator</a> is one of the best blog name generators available online. You can use our easy tool to find the perfect name for your blog or website. Simply enter in 1 or 2 keywords, hit the <strong>Generate Names</strong> button, and voila! You&#8217;re instantly presented with a wide array of blog name ideas that include your desired keyword(s). </p>\n<p>With this tool, you can also check the domain name availability instantly with Bluehost. This means you can snatch up that blog name quickly, before anyone else has the chance to steal it.</p>\n<p>Plus, Bluehost is offering an awesome deal for IsItWP readers. You can get a free domain name, SSL certificate, and discounted hosting that starts at only $2.75 per month. With this sweet deal, you can start your blog today! Click here to get this <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >exclusive deal with Bluehost</a>. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/domain-name-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get Blog Name Ideas with IsItWP Domain Name Generator &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.nameboy.com/\" target=\"_blank\">2. NameBoy</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.nameboy.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/nameboy-blog-name-generator.jpg\" alt=\"nameboy-best-blog-name-generator\" width=\"740\" height=\"303\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230442\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/nameboy-blog-name-generator.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/nameboy-blog-name-generator-300x123.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.nameboy.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Nameboy</a> is the oldest and most popular domain name generator in the world, so it&#8217;s a great tool to use to find the perfect name for your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/blog-vs-website/\">blog or website</a>. Nameboy started in 1999 and their goal is to help people find creative business names for their company, product, or blog so they can turn their ideas into reality. </p>\n<p>Nameboy&#8217;s domain and blog name generator analyzes the keywords you enter into the domain name search field and provides you with suggestions for the best domain name ideas for your business or blog. They also offer the ability to check domain availability with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Bluehost</a> as well as provide expert tips on how to choose the best domain name.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.nameboy.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get Blog Name Ideas with Nameboy &raquo;</a> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify-business-name-generator/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >3. Shopify Business Name Generator</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify-business-name-generator/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/shopify-business-name-generator.jpg\" alt=\"shopify-business-name-generator\" width=\"740\" height=\"309\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230445\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/shopify-business-name-generator.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/shopify-business-name-generator-300x125.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify-business-name-generator/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Shopify Business Name Generator</a>, from one of the most <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\">popular eCommerce plugins</a>, is another awesome blog name generator you can use to find the perfect blog name. </p>\n<p>With this free business/blog name generator you can easily find the right name for your blog. You can enter a word that you want to include in your blog/business name, hit the <strong>Generate names</strong> button, and instantly receive a ton of blog name ideas that are checked for domain name availability. </p>\n<p>You can then click on the blog name idea you like the most and the tool gives you steps for reserving the name on Shopify. This option is perfect if you plan on selling products on your blog. You can also take that domain name and register and purchase it on any other site. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify-business-name-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get Blog Name Ideas with Shopify Business Name Generator &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/domain-com/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >4. Domain.com</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/domain-com/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/domain-website.jpg\" alt=\"domain-best-blog-name-generator\" width=\"740\" height=\"364\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230450\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/domain-website.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/domain-website-300x148.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p>On <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/domain-com/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Domain.com</a> you can find the perfect name for your blog and purchase the domain, all in 1 place. Start by entering a domain name idea into the domain name search field. If your preferred blog name is taken, Domain.com will then give you a bunch of similar blog name ideas that are available. Along with the domain name ideas, they also display the price for the domain names. </p>\n<p>When you find a domain name that you like, you can add it to your cart. At the same time, you have the option of purchasing a Google G Suite email that matches your domain name, powerful web hosting, SSL certificate, and a SiteLock plan to protect your website from malware, hackers, and viruses. </p>\n<p>So, you can find the perfect blog name and start <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">building your website</a> all at once.  </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/domain-com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get Blog Name Ideas with Domain.com &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/godaddy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. GoDaddy.com</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/godaddy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/godaddy-name-generator.jpg\" alt=\"godaddy-blog-name-generator\" width=\"740\" height=\"351\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230451\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/godaddy-name-generator.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/godaddy-name-generator-300x142.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/godaddy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">GoDaddy</a> is a well-known and popular choice for purchasing a domain name and web hosting but they also have a great business name generator tool that will help you find a great name for your blog. Type a couple keywords into the search field and click the <strong>Search</strong> button. For example, if you enter the keyword &#8220;knitting&#8221;, the tool will tell you that the domain knitting.com is already taken, and then provide you with a ton of name options that are available with the keyword &#8220;knitting&#8221; in them. </p>\n<p>GoDaddy also displays the cost of the domain name too. Once you find the blog name that&#8217;s right for you, you can then add it to your cart and purchase it right away. As you&#8217;re checking out, GoDaddy also gives you the option of starting your website right away with their free trial of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/godaddy-website-builder/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >GoDaddy website builder</a>. </p>\n<p>With GoDaddy you can find and purchase the perfect domain name for your blog and start building your website right away, so you can have your blog up and running in less than 1 hour. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/godaddy//\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get Blog Name Ideas with GoDaddy &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/namecheap/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >6. NameCheap.com</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/namecheap/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/namecheap-blog-name-generator.jpg\" alt=\"namecheap-blog-name-generator\" width=\"740\" height=\"253\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230452\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/namecheap-blog-name-generator.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/namecheap-blog-name-generator-300x103.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/namecheap/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >NameCheap.com</a> is another one of the best blog name generators available. This tool is best if you already have a blog name in mind. You can type in the blog name you&#8217;re thinking of using and NameCheap will tell you if the domain name is available. </p>\n<p>If your preferred <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/domain-name-work/\">domain name</a> is already taken, NameCheap will give you options for domain name extensions that are available. For instance, if Fishing.com is already taken, this tool will give you give you ideas like Fishing.online or Fishing.fun. Although, we recommend sticking with the extension .com because it&#8217;s the most well-known, trusted, and easily remembered. </p>\n<p>If you find the domain name you want and it&#8217;s available, you can add it to your cart and purchase it right away. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/namecheap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get Blog Name Ideas with NameCheap.com &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://domainwheel.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. DomainWheel</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://domainwheel.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/domainwheel.jpg\" alt=\"domainwheel-blog-name-generator\" width=\"740\" height=\"287\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230454\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/domainwheel.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/domainwheel-300x116.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://domainwheel.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">DomainWheel</a> is one of the newer blog name generators available online. Simply enter in 1 or 2 keywords into the search field and press the <strong>Search Domain</strong> button. DomainWheel will then give you an assortment of the best available blog name ideas relating to those keywords. </p>\n<p>On top of those related blog name ideas, DomainWheel also gives you a number of random blog name ideas. They also provide a list of ideas that rhyme with the keywords you entered to inspire you further. If you&#8217;re really stuck on what blog name to choose, this is a great blog name generator to try out. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://domainwheel.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get Blog Name Ideas with DomainWheel &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://instantdomainsearch.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. InstantDomainSearch.com</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://instantdomainsearch.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/instant-domain-search.jpg\" alt=\"instant-domain-search\" width=\"740\" height=\"398\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230455\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/instant-domain-search.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/instant-domain-search-300x161.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://instantdomainsearch.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">InstantDomainSearch.com</a> is the last on our list for the best blog name generators. With this blog name generator, domain name search results appear instantly as you type your keywords in the search field.</p>\n<p>In the search results, you can see extensions that are available for your desired blog name, new blog name ideas in the generator section, and related domain names that are for sale. </p>\n<p>If you find a domain name that you like, you can purchase it by clicking the link on the site that leads you right to GoDaddy.  </p>\n<p>With these awesome blog name generators, you can now start the process of finding the perfect name for your blog. With these tools finding the best blog name will not only be easy, but fun too. If you enjoyed this article, check out our other post on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-blogging-platforms-beginners-compared/\">Best Blogging Platforms for Beginners (Compared)</a>. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-blog-name-generators/\">8 BEST Blog Name Generators to Find the Perfect Blog Name</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-blog-name-generators/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:28:\"https://www.isitwp.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:19:{s:6:\"server\";s:17:\"Sucuri/Cloudproxy\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Thu, 21 Mar 2019 10:59:28 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:34:\"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8\";s:11:\"x-sucuri-id\";s:5:\"13003\";s:16:\"x-xss-protection\";s:13:\"1; mode=block\";s:15:\"x-frame-options\";s:10:\"SAMEORIGIN\";s:22:\"x-content-type-options\";s:7:\"nosniff\";s:25:\"strict-transport